Inspired by Final Fantasy, Legend of Zelda, and Kingdom Hearts, this project embodies the vision of all those identities into an afro-fantasy lens. I believed in making these ethereal dreamers that live in their own universe, created from VR and 3D music. https://t.co/ACxDrAZvni
